  • Constructor Details

    • Cinema

      public Cinema(int cineplexId, int code, int height, int width, Cinema.showClassOptions c, String seatConfiguration)
      Constructor for creating cinema object with the ability to store meta information regarding cinema
      Parameters:
      cineplexId - The cineplex ID
      code - The code of cinema
      height - The height of seating arrangement in cinema
      width - The width of seating arrangement in cinema
      c - The class of specific cinema
      seatConfiguration - The seating configurations consisting multiple type of seats and non-seats such as aisle and stairs, arbitrarily interchangeable
